data.description: This beautiful 4 Bed, 3 Bath Home is ready for it's new owner! Located in the peaceful Cherokee Club Subdivision of Jacksonville, you will love this home's curb appeal. The sprawling front yard is well manicured, featuring mature trees that highlight the stately appearance of the home. Once inside, you will love the many features that it provides. The kitchen has quartz countertops and an island, with a breakfast area and opens nicely into the over-sized living room with fireplace. The dining room is massive, offering an opportunity to host large gatherings and meals. Downstairs, there is also a media room, full guest bathroom, and a laundry room with storage. The master bedroom provides plenty of space for a sitting area, and you will love the master bath, with its gorgeous countertops, big shower, and walk in closet. The guest bedrooms are large, and the house boasts plenty of storage. Once outside, you can enjoy your time in the screened in porch or on your outdoor deck. All of this, not to mention the 2 car garage, storage shed, and easy access to the golf course. Call today for your personal showing!
